CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784047674
OL,3,CGuilty plea for health and safety
OL,4,Cbreaches after man dies at climbing
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FA multi-agency response involved six
OL,8,Fcrews from Cumbria Fire and Rescue
OL,9,FService as well as Keswick Mountain
OL,10,FRescue Team and the North West Air
OL,11,FAmbulance.
OL,13,FHe died several days later at the
OL,14,FCumberland Infirmary in Carlisle.
OL,16,FCompany director of King Kong Climbing
OL,17,FCentre LTD Paul Cornforth was charged
OL,18,Fwith failing to ensure that Mr
OL,19,FO'Keeffe was not exposed to risks to
OL,20,Fhis health and safety.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
