OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784047674
OL,3,CGuilty plea for health and safety
OL,4,Cbreaches after man dies at climbing
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FOn behalf of King Kong Climbing LTD,
OL,8,FCornforth pleaded guilty to this
OL,9,Fcharge, appearing remotely at
OL,10,FNewcastle Crown Court this morning,
OL,11,FMonday 13 July.
OL,13,FHe faces an additional charge, that
OL,14,Fthe offence was committed with his
OL,15,Fconsent or connivance, or was
OL,16,Fattributable to his neglect. He has
OL,17,Fpreviously pleaded not guilty to this
OL,18,Fcharge.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
